      <title>内塔尼亚胡说，他正在解雇Shin Bet安全负责人Ronen Bar</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/netanyahu-says-he-s-firing-shin-bet-security-chief-ronen-bar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）表示，他计划解雇家庭安全服务局负责人Shin Bet的负责人Ronen Bar，他与他对10月7日袭击的责任，人质谈判以及对与卡塔尔的联系的调查感到吵架。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/netanyahu-says-he-s-firing-shin-bet-security-chief-ronen-bar</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 18:17:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其的埃尔多安（Erdogan）呼吁特朗普审查有关国防的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/turkey-s-erdogan-calls-on-trump-to-review-sanctions-on-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）敦促美国取消2020年对其国防工业实施的制裁，并呼吁将其恢复在跨国F-35倡议中，该计划发展并产生下一代军事飞机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/turkey-s-erdogan-calls-on-trump-to-review-sanctions-on-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 16:08:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>持续不必担心市场，呼吁更正健康</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/bessent-says-he-s-not-worried-about-market-corrections-healthy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）是前对冲基金经理，他说，由于美国试图重塑其经济政策，他并不担心最近的经济下滑，从股票市场擦掉了数万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/bessent-says-he-s-not-worried-about-market-corrections-healthy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:22:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普驱逐了数百名敌人的法院谴责法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/trump-deports-hundreds-under-enemies-act-as-court-rebukes-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府表示，它逮捕了委内瑞拉的特伦·德·阿拉古亚帮派成千上万的据称成员，送往萨尔瓦多，即使联邦法官下令停止一些驱逐出境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/trump-deports-hundreds-under-enemies-act-as-court-rebukes-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:19:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格斯说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/us-attacks-on-houthis-will-be-unrelenting-hegseth-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼负责人皮特·赫格斯斯（Pete Hegseth）周日表示，在唐纳德·赫斯斯（Pete Hegseth）下天，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统下令在中东下令新的业务后，美国对也门的军事罢工将“不屈不挠”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/us-attacks-on-houthis-will-be-unrelenting-hegseth-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特使说，特朗普本周可能会在乌克兰与普京交谈。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/trump-may-speak-to-putin-on-ukraine-this-week-us-envoy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统可能会在本周与俄罗斯领导人弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）交谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/trump-may-speak-to-putin-on-ukraine-this-week-us-envoy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 14:05:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国的贝鲁（Bayrou）规定，将退休年龄恢复到62</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/france-s-bayrou-rules-out-bringing-retirement-age-back-to-62</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁（Francois Bayrou）以养老金制度的财务状况为由，将法国退休年龄带到62岁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/france-s-bayrou-rules-out-bringing-retirement-age-back-to-62</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 14:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NBC民意调查显示，选民对特朗普的经济感到乐观又恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/nbc-poll-shows-us-voters-upbeat-yet-souring-on-state-of-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NBC新闻民意测验显示，即使唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）第二任期的开始，选民也开始对美国经济状况感到恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/nbc-poll-shows-us-voters-upbeat-yet-souring-on-state-of-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 13:22:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度在与新西兰进行贸易协议的会谈，因为美国关税织机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/india-in-talks-with-new-zealand-on-trade-deal-as-us-tariffs-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着国家寻求加强经济关系，印度已经开始就与新西兰达成的自由贸易协定进行谈判，这是全球贸易不确定性的增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/india-in-talks-with-new-zealand-on-trade-deal-as-us-tariffs-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 12:03:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国否认它将大使馆的工作人员从摩加迪沙（Mogadishu）撤出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/us-denies-it-s-pulling-staff-from-somali-embassy-in-mogadishu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻摩加迪沙大使馆否认，由于东非国家的处境越来越不稳定，因此开始将员工从索马里撤出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/us-denies-it-s-pulling-staff-from-somali-embassy-in-mogadishu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 11:35:56 GMT</pubDate>
